<br>
Its sad to see people I thought had character or integrity stay in guilds that continue to disrespect other people. If we all played on a LAN or near each other in RL, this kind of thing would not happen, but some people feel safe about doing these kinds of things to other people because they worst that can happen to them will happen in a game.<br>
